## Accessibility Commitment

This project is committed to providing an inclusive experience for all users.
The software implements WCAG 2.1 AAA standards and follows accessibility
best practices. Any accessibility issues found should be reported as bugs
and will be prioritized for immediate resolution.

## Data Privacy & LGPD Compliance

This software respects user privacy and complies with Brazilian LGPD
(Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados) requirements. Personal data handling
follows privacy-by-design principles and user consent mechanisms.

## Academic Use

This project was developed as part of academic research at Universidade
Franciscana (UFN). Academic use, research, and educational implementations
are especially encouraged. Please cite appropriately if used in academic work:

```
Projeto Aproxima - Plataforma de Acompanhamento Pré-natal Acessível
Universidade Franciscana (UFN), 2024
Available at: https://github.com/KallebyX/aproxima
```

## Healthcare Disclaimer

This software is intended for educational and informational purposes related
to prenatal care. It is not intended to replace professional medical advice,
diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of qualified healthcare
providers with any questions regarding medical conditions or treatments.

